creator: Dengun
descriptionHtml:
The Pine Cliffs Resort Official App is the ultimate experience to discover a Luxury Collection Resort. A five star hotel with luxurious services and Real Estate. With this app you will be able to:
- Find all the events around the resort
- Discover all the 12 Restaurants and Bars of the resort
- Book your restaurant
- Book your accommodation
- Book your Tennis and Golf lessons
- Explore the Real Estate and Resort galleries
- Share your experience with family and friends
- Make use of the latest offers
- Get to know the weather in real time with forecast of three days
- Get the latest Concierge tips
- Receive on your mobile device offers at the resort on time
descriptionShort: A unique place in the World. Your Home.
